      "Text": "Security update for the Linux Kernel (Live Patch 20 for SLE 15 SP3)",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for the Linux Kernel 5.3.18-150300_59_76 fixes several issues.\n\nThe following security issues were fixed:\n\n- CVE-2022-3564: Fixed use-after-free in l2cap_core.c of the Bluetooth component (bsc#1206314).\n- CVE-2023-0179: Fixed incorrect arithmetics when fetching VLAN header bits (bsc#1207139).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
